@startuml
title Campaign State Transition Diagram

[*] --> StartCampaign

state StartCampaign
state Running
state PrepareAdverts
state ApprovedAdverts
state CompleteCampaign
state PaymentHandling
state RefundGenerated
state AwaitingBalance
state Paid
state Archived

StartCampaign --> Running : Campaign started

Running --> PrepareAdverts : Prepare adverts
PrepareAdverts --> ApprovedAdverts : Approve adverts
ApprovedAdverts --> Running : Schedule adverts

Running --> CompleteCampaign : All adverts finished
CompleteCampaign --> PaymentHandling : Process payment

PaymentHandling --> RefundGenerated : Amount paid less than required
PaymentHandling --> AwaitingBalance : Amount paid more than required
PaymentHandling --> Paid : Full amount paid

Paid --> Archived : Archive campaign
RefundGenerated --> Archived : Archive campaign
AwaitingBalance --> Paid : Correct balance settled

Archived --> [*]

@enduml
